erlaudiotag - parse audio file metadata tags in Erlang
Copyright (C) 2009 Hans Ulrich Niedermann <hun@n-dimensional.de>
http://github.com/ndim/

Immediate Goals:
 * Get useful metadata information from audio files.
 * Write original or modified metadata to audio files.
 * Fix the brokenly tagged MP3 files from my podcast subscription list
   so that they work properly with my digital audio player (DAP).

Eventual Goals:
 * Nice API
 * Nice architecture
 * Automatically fix MP3 files arriving in a certain directory
   tree when they turn up (using inotify/FAM/gamin).
 * Make the metadata useful for putting audio files onto
   web pages.

